# 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ICanHearYou.git
cd ICanHearYou
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python scripts/download_models.py
python src/main_app.py
```

---

# 🔮 Christman Voice SDK (Private)

ToneScore™ • Adaptive Response Mode • VoiceSDK

```python
result = sdk.synthesize("I'm still here, baby.", tone_score=tonescore.score)
```

> SDK is proprietary. Approval required.

